	<P><FONT FACE="Arial">At many New Force rallies, besides using the two main flags shown at the top left, a more traditional Italian Nazi Flag with the Sun Wheel (Type #5 and Type #6) has also been used both in red and black backgrounds. A NSDAP-style flag with the letters &quot;FN&quot; on a white disc also exists in variants of black and red colors, in fact, this variant can be found more frequently on the Web than the earlier one.</P> 
