<p><FONT FACE="Arial">In late 2013, a new flag with meander within a wreath, surrounded with
the full name of the party, has appeared. Its field is red and the charges are black, fimbriated white. The earliest photos can be found is also being increasingly used abroad, by ultra-rightists wishing to show the support to like-minded "persecutees", considering the criminal charges against the party and its members, a number of which was brought since 2012, merely as the "persecution" campaign.</p></TD>
